[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960", "name": "car", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?m=1644885960", "title": "汽车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/car", "topics": 3232, "footer": "", "header": "关于买车、开车及汽车文化的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Car", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960", "stars": 2275, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 176, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 502880, "username": "Tilie", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Tilie", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a2e9970d85669a0258387e24b0dfea26?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a2e9970d85669a0258387e24b0dfea26?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a2e9970d85669a0258387e24b0dfea26?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1596844150, "last_modified": 1779507957, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "ltyj2003", "last_touched": 1779587475, "title": "作为程序员，你愿意为“0 AI 代码介入”的汽车支付溢价吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1214894", "created": 1779508198, "deleted": 0, "content": "大家好，我是做嵌入式开发的。先给纯软方向的同学铺垫个背景：基本上现在能通电的设备都会带 MCU ，也都有代码在上面运行。\r\n\r\n结合目前的行业现状，我想和大家探讨一个细思极恐的问题：\r\n\r\n### **现状：防不胜防，汽车底层代码正被 AI 全面渗透**\r\n我可以很肯定地说，只要是今年新出的车，100% 已经包含了 AI 生成的代码。而且很多时候，这已经是避无可避的：\r\n* **上游污染（被动使用）：** 现在的 AI 渗透是全方位的，很多 MCU 原厂提供的 SDK 源码里，本身就已经混入了 AI 生成的代码。哪怕下游车企的程序员完全不用 AI ，只要基于官方库做开发，就已经“被动”使用了 AI 代码。\r\n* **下游外包（主动使用）：** 汽车行业有着极度细分的分包特性。很多底层设备的最终逻辑代码，可能就是由刚毕业没几年的应届生，为了赶工期用着各种 AI 工具（甚至是国产 AI ）直接跑出来的。\r\n\r\n### **隐患：缺乏 Review 的黑盒**\r\n难听点说，由于层层外包和赶进度，很多这种 AI 参与的代码根本没人严格 Review 。它纯粹是一个跑得通就行的“黑盒”。\r\n它的控制范围有多广？\r\n* **轻则：** 车上所有能被按下的按钮、空调开关、车窗升降。\r\n* **重则：** 转向系统控制、ESP 车身稳定系统、甚至是碰撞后的应急解锁。\r\n\r\n### **我的问题：**\r\n如果未来有车厂以此为卖点，宣传自己的系统是 **“100% 纯人类手写、0 AI 介入、经过严格人工 Code Review”**，大家愿意为这种安全性（或者说安全感）额外付费吗？\r\n还是说，大家更愿意相信车厂的黑盒 Testcase 覆盖度足够高，只要价格越便宜越好？想听听各位 V 友的看法。", "content_rendered": "<p>大家好，我是做嵌入式开发的。先给纯软方向的同学铺垫个背景：基本上现在能通电的设备都会带 MCU ，也都有代码在上面运行。</p>\n<p>结合目前的行业现状，我想和大家探讨一个细思极恐的问题：</p>\n<h3><strong>现状：防不胜防，汽车底层代码正被 AI 全面渗透</strong></h3>\n<p>我可以很肯定地说，只要是今年新出的车，100% 已经包含了 AI 生成的代码。而且很多时候，这已经是避无可避的：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>上游污染（被动使用）：</strong> 现在的 AI 渗透是全方位的，很多 MCU 原厂提供的 SDK 源码里，本身就已经混入了 AI 生成的代码。哪怕下游车企的程序员完全不用 AI ，只要基于官方库做开发，就已经“被动”使用了 AI 代码。</li>\n<li><strong>下游外包（主动使用）：</strong> 汽车行业有着极度细分的分包特性。很多底层设备的最终逻辑代码，可能就是由刚毕业没几年的应届生，为了赶工期用着各种 AI 工具（甚至是国产 AI ）直接跑出来的。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>隐患：缺乏 Review 的黑盒</strong></h3>\n<p>难听点说，由于层层外包和赶进度，很多这种 AI 参与的代码根本没人严格 Review 。它纯粹是一个跑得通就行的“黑盒”。\n它的控制范围有多广？</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>轻则：</strong> 车上所有能被按下的按钮、空调开关、车窗升降。</li>\n<li><strong>重则：</strong> 转向系统控制、ESP 车身稳定系统、甚至是碰撞后的应急解锁。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>我的问题：</strong></h3>\n<p>如果未来有车厂以此为卖点，宣传自己的系统是 <strong>“100% 纯人类手写、0 AI 介入、经过严格人工 Code Review”</strong>，大家愿意为这种安全性（或者说安全感）额外付费吗？\n还是说，大家更愿意相信车厂的黑盒 Testcase 覆盖度足够高，只要价格越便宜越好？想听听各位 V 友的看法。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779514186, "replies": 70, "id": 1214894}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1777132346", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1777132346", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 238743, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4488, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 397519, "username": "shanex", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/shanex", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cfae071df818fb86a98220d9b73c242e?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cfae071df818fb86a98220d9b73c242e?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cfae071df818fb86a98220d9b73c242e?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1554125290, "last_modified": 1744865434, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "ltyj2003", "last_touched": 1779587693, "title": "有没有不用买车也能让新手熟练掌握开车驾驶的办法？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1214887", "created": 1779507021, "deleted": 0, "content": "10 年驾照从未上过路，迫切地想开车自驾，但是处于没啥经验，心中胆怯。\r\n\r\n家里本来计划过继一辆旧车给我，但是考虑到必要性和后续使用成本，没有要。\r\n\r\n其实用车的场景有限，后续还是想租车玩，所以就面临一个问题，租车之前怎么熟练的掌握驾驶\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n有没有同样经历的朋友", "content_rendered": "<p>10 年驾照从未上过路，迫切地想开车自驾，但是处于没啥经验，心中胆怯。</p>\n<p>家里本来计划过继一辆旧车给我，但是考虑到必要性和后续使用成本，没有要。</p>\n<p>其实用车的场景有限，后续还是想租车玩，所以就面临一个问题，租车之前怎么熟练的掌握驾驶</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>有没有同样经历的朋友</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779507021, "replies": 55, "id": 1214887}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1777132346", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1777132346", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 238743, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4488, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 681499, "username": "lzaske9", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lzaske9", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "天津", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d8a6/0a40/681499_mini.png?m=1776737971", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d8a6/0a40/681499_normal.png?m=1776737971", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d8a6/0a40/681499_large.png?m=1776737971", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d8a6/0a40/681499_xlarge.png?m=1776737971", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d8a6/0a40/681499_xxlarge.png?m=1776737971", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d8a6/0a40/681499_xxxlarge.png?m=1776737971", "created": 1711117654, "last_modified": 1776737971, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "june4", "last_touched": 1779588262, "title": "颈椎病有啥办法吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1214938", "created": 1779524970, "deleted": 0, "content": "坐标天津 24  \r\n\r\n半个月前确认颈椎曲度消失，头晕，只是简单拍了个 DR  \r\n西医就开了一堆止疼药  \r\n\r\n之后可能是受凉了，右侧肩胛骨和后颈连接处开始疼  \r\n简单动作都会牵着疼  \r\n去看中医，开了刮痧、拔罐、放血，还有中药外敷  \r\n效果不好说，不确定是自己恢复了还是有用  \r\n四五天以后基本没什么反应了  \r\n\r\n昨天突然又开始疼，今天开始头晕、手麻  \r\n明天约了天津医科大学总医院骨外科  \r\n\r\n真的好折磨人  \r\nV 友有同样情况的吗？有什么好办法吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>坐标天津 24  </p>\n<p>半个月前确认颈椎曲度消失，头晕，只是简单拍了个 DR<br/>\n西医就开了一堆止疼药  </p>\n<p>之后可能是受凉了，右侧肩胛骨和后颈连接处开始疼<br/>\n简单动作都会牵着疼<br/>\n去看中医，开了刮痧、拔罐、放血，还有中药外敷<br/>\n效果不好说，不确定是自己恢复了还是有用<br/>\n四五天以后基本没什么反应了  </p>\n<p>昨天突然又开始疼，今天开始头晕、手麻<br/>\n明天约了天津医科大学总医院骨外科  </p>\n<p>真的好折磨人<br/>\nV 友有同样情况的吗？有什么好办法吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779525264, "replies": 40, "id": 1214938}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71188, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9688, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 253373, "username": "cubecube", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/cubecube", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/67f5/7629/253373_mini.png?m=1766041928", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/67f5/7629/253373_normal.png?m=1766041928", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/67f5/7629/253373_large.png?m=1766041928", "created": 1504941340, "last_modified": 1766041928, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "hongye", "last_touched": 1779549600, "title": "qwen3.7-max 的代码能力提升非常大", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1214878", "created": 1779503711, "deleted": 0, "content": "高强度用了一天，体感上和 glm-5.1 不相上下了。相对于 3.6 自主分析和解决能力飞跃\r\n如果各位只有国内的稳定接入源的话，可以试试看。", "content_rendered": "高强度用了一天，体感上和 glm-5.1 不相上下了。相对于 3.6 自主分析和解决能力飞跃<br />如果各位只有国内的稳定接入源的话，可以试试看。", "last_modified": 1779503711, "replies": 35, "id": 1214878}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10899, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2326, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 559930, "username": "hahade", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hahade", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7cfe/a737/559930_mini.png?m=1635487272", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7cfe/a737/559930_normal.png?m=1635487272", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7cfe/a737/559930_large.png?m=1635487272", "created": 1635391001, "last_modified": 1635487272, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "hahade", "last_touched": 1779563287, "title": "小区有人高空抛物，差点砸到人。是不是无解？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1214958", "created": 1779533785, "deleted": 0, "content": "有人晚上从楼上扔了一个瓷碗，差点把业主砸到了。然后这个业主打了多次 110 电话，居然打不通。看业主群里面说物业后面打了电话，说是转给派出所处理了。也不知真假。\r\n这个小区去年就已经安装了对上的摄像头，物业也没有把监控视频发出来。我个人猜测可能这个摄像头只是一个样子，可能连电都没有通。\r\n\r\n这几天想了想，一个人要想做坏事，有一万种办法，防不胜防。另外，似乎大家对不发生在自己身上的事情都不关心。估计已经不了了之了。", "content_rendered": "<p>有人晚上从楼上扔了一个瓷碗，差点把业主砸到了。然后这个业主打了多次 110 电话，居然打不通。看业主群里面说物业后面打了电话，说是转给派出所处理了。也不知真假。\n这个小区去年就已经安装了对上的摄像头，物业也没有把监控视频发出来。我个人猜测可能这个摄像头只是一个样子，可能连电都没有通。</p>\n<p>这几天想了想，一个人要想做坏事，有一万种办法，防不胜防。另外，似乎大家对不发生在自己身上的事情都不关心。估计已经不了了之了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779533785, "replies": 25, "id": 1214958}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/5090/5d7b/1314_large.png?m=1769400224", "name": "display", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/5090/5d7b/1314_normal.png?m=1769400224", "title": "显示器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/display", "topics": 9, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "显示器", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/5090/5d7b/1314_mini.png?m=1769400224", "stars": 2, "founder_id": 50942, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1314, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 777785, "username": "adz1181014499", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/adz1181014499", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0097d2b884216cfea9ff0a2c9584716a?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0097d2b884216cfea9ff0a2c9584716a?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0097d2b884216cfea9ff0a2c9584716a?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1765432543, "last_modified": 1765432543, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "whusnoopy", "last_touched": 1779562979, "title": "双屏配置，你们都用的什么组合？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1214899", "created": 1779509754, "deleted": 0, "content": "看来看去，好像用各种组合的都大有人在\r\n有 32+27 竖屏\r\n有 32+24 竖屏\r\n有 27+27 双显\r\n有 27+24 副屏\r\n长久来看你们更推荐哪一个呀？\r\n另外就大家工作流的需求来看是不是没必要考虑带鱼屏？", "content_rendered": "<p>看来看去，好像用各种组合的都大有人在\n有 32+27 竖屏\n有 32+24 竖屏\n有 27+27 双显\n有 27+24 副屏\n长久来看你们更推荐哪一个呀？\n另外就大家工作流的需求来看是不是没必要考虑带鱼屏？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779509785, "replies": 24, "id": 1214899}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1777132346", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1777132346", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 238743, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4488, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 525301, "username": "mingtdlb", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/mingtdlb", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1067/fd49/525301_mini.png?m=1742795473", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1067/fd49/525301_normal.png?m=1742795473", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1067/fd49/525301_large.png?m=1742795473", "created": 1608735043, "last_modified": 1742795473, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "bowencool", "last_touched": 1779549985, "title": "大家用 codex、Antigravity 都开 tun 吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1214920", "created": 1779518984, "deleted": 0, "content": "我在想有没有能根据应用去代理，这样就不用开 tun 了。因为开 tun 之后，有时候 ping 域名都是 198.18.x.x 的 ip ，又要去关 tun 不方便\r\n\r\n我是 win11", "content_rendered": "<p>我在想有没有能根据应用去代理，这样就不用开 tun 了。因为开 tun 之后，有时候 ping 域名都是 198.18.x.x 的 ip ，又要去关 tun 不方便</p>\n<p>我是 win11</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779518984, "replies": 22, "id": 1214920}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6b18/0037/1013_large.png?m=1699513459", "name": "jd", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6b18/0037/1013_normal.png?m=1699513459", "title": "京东", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/jd", "topics": 1979, "footer": "", "header": "关于使用 jd.com 过程中遇到的问题的讨论", "title_alternative": "京东", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6b18/0037/1013_mini.png?m=1699513459", "stars": 226, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1013, "parent_node_name": "mmm"}, "member": {"id": 655340, "username": "kierankihn", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kierankihn", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_mini.png?m=1755360643", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_normal.png?m=1755360643", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_large.png?m=1755360643", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_xlarge.png?m=1755360643", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_xxlarge.png?m=1755360643", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_xxxlarge.png?m=1755360643", "created": 1697684491, "last_modified": 1755360643, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Wyearn", "last_touched": 1779587985, "title": "吐槽京东自营的罗技售后问题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1214960", "created": 1779534661, "deleted": 0, "content": "不到一年前在京东买的 MX Master 3s ，最近出现了右键失灵+双击的问题，因为还在保修期内，遂找京东客服。\r\n\r\n在京东上提交售后之后，接到 025-5207-6007 打来的电话，要求我把鼠标寄到当地的罗技售后，并且客服那边把京东的服务单关闭了。另外还要求给京东的服务单好评，才能返寄出的邮费。\r\n\r\n正常的流程不应该是提交服务单之后京东直接上门取件吗，不是很懂为什么需要这么操作。", "content_rendered": "<p>不到一年前在京东买的 MX Master 3s ，最近出现了右键失灵+双击的问题，因为还在保修期内，遂找京东客服。</p>\n<p>在京东上提交售后之后，接到 025-5207-6007 打来的电话，要求我把鼠标寄到当地的罗技售后，并且客服那边把京东的服务单关闭了。另外还要求给京东的服务单好评，才能返寄出的邮费。</p>\n<p>正常的流程不应该是提交服务单之后京东直接上门取件吗，不是很懂为什么需要这么操作。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779534661, "replies": 22, "id": 1214960}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_large.png?m=1751736785", "name": "openai", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_normal.png?m=1751736785", "title": "OpenAI", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/openai", "topics": 3914, "footer": "", "header": "关于 OpenAI 旗下产品 GPT，DALL·E，和 ChatGPT 的讨论。请不要在 V2EX 的回复中粘贴复制来自 AI 生成的文本。", "title_alternative": "OpenAI", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_mini.png?m=1751736785", "stars": 3088, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1135, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 428568, "username": "layxy", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/layxy", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/57b94f7f153f3745286c0b8db7131786?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/57b94f7f153f3745286c0b8db7131786?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/57b94f7f153f3745286c0b8db7131786?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1562813759, "last_modified": 1775727309, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "gogocome", "last_touched": 1779589608, "title": "openai 周限又重置了，已经放弃 claude 了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1215013", "created": 1779581082, "deleted": 0, "content": "好订阅，不易封号，gpt5.5 和 codex 使用体验顶级，额度量大管饱，还经常找理由重置额度，针对正规订阅的付费用户，体验感觉各方面都比 A\\要好，claudecode 的优势感觉现在也不明显了，codex 已经取消上下文小圆圈显示，让你尽情使用，其自动上下文压缩目前在一众工具默认配置里也是顶尖的，订阅的性价比我觉得比国内一众的 plan 套餐还要好", "content_rendered": "<p>好订阅，不易封号，gpt5.5 和 codex 使用体验顶级，额度量大管饱，还经常找理由重置额度，针对正规订阅的付费用户，体验感觉各方面都比 A\\要好，claudecode 的优势感觉现在也不明显了，codex 已经取消上下文小圆圈显示，让你尽情使用，其自动上下文压缩目前在一众工具默认配置里也是顶尖的，订阅的性价比我觉得比国内一众的 plan 套餐还要好</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779581082, "replies": 21, "id": 1215013}]